  "industry_note": "HfC (Hafnium Carbide, NaCl-structure) — **highest melting point known compound** (Tm ≈ 3900°C). ρ 12.2-12.7 g/cc. σf 270-400 / E 461 / KIC 4.0 / Mohs 9.5 / Tmax 3000°C inert (oxidation 시 HfO₂ 형성 1700°C 이상). Hypersonic vehicle leading edge (Mach 7+ — X-43A, X-51 Waverider), 핵 추진 (nuclear thermal rocket throat), 진공 chamber electrode. 매우 비싸 ($2000-5000/kg). Hf-Ta-C 같은 ternary 더 high-Tm 가능 (4200°C)."
